Gosh, I can't believe
a place like this exists.

21
00:01:14,010 --> 00:01:16,880
For once, he didn't get scammed.

22
00:01:17,080 --> 00:01:20,350
I'm just so glad
he can sing his heart out here.

23
00:01:24,060 --> 00:01:25,720
Are you okay?

24
00:01:26,520 --> 00:01:28,360
That weak ankle of yours...

25
